Hi. I am a recruiter for TEEMA. I have a hiring client in Scottsdale, AZ that needs a Sr. Ruby Developer. Rate 100k+ 
Expert Ruby development
Linux, OOP, Rails, SQL, JavaScript, HTML
PHP, Postgres, MySQL, SQL Server, ElasticSearch, Apache, Nginx, Bash preferred.
Resume to jgarcia@teemagroup.com
Jill
Thank you for connecting. Interested in role mentioned? Referrals?
Sorry, already got submitted there and they ignored me.
I just looked you up. Please contact Tracy again to find out the status. Was it the TEEMA rep ignoring you or the Client? Please keep me posted.
I reached out to Nicholas who said he was hiring for the position but never replied.
Let me figure out what's going on.... did you send anyone your resume at TEEMA?
Oh yeah. Looks like we got hung up on the programming test. Now how is it possible for me to hold a job if I don't know how to program?

This is for a different role, it looks like. Please contact Jeff Lin about this role so you can be a candidate for it.... there are a few roles there. You might qualify for a different one.
Jill
